languages.text: "Я хотел{mf||а} сказать, что все это не стоит моего внимания. Так что расслабься, ты мне больше не интересен".
"What I mean is that none of this is worth my attention. You can stop worrying — I am not interested in you anymore."

languages.text: "Ich meine, dass all das meiner Aufmerksamkeit nicht würdig ist. Ihr könnt aufhören, Euch Sorgen zu machen, ich habe kein Interesse mehr an Euch."
languages.original_text: "What I mean is that none of this is worth my attention. You can stop worrying — I am not interested in you anymore."

languages.text: « Je veux dire que cette histoire n'est pas digne de mon attention. Inutile de vous en préoccuper, je ne m'intéresse plus à vous. »
languages.original_text: "What I mean is that none of this is worth my attention. You can stop worrying — I am not interested in you anymore."

languages.text: «Lo que quiero decir es que nada de eso merece mi atención. Puede dejar de preocuparse; ya no me interesa usted en lo más mínimo».
languages.original_text: "What I mean is that none of this is worth my attention. You can stop worrying — I am not interested in you anymore."

languages.text: “我的意思是说，这一切根本不值得我费心关注。你不用再担心了，我已经对你失去兴趣了。”
languages.original_text: "What I mean is that none of this is worth my attention. You can stop worrying — I am not interested in you anymore."

languages.text: "Demek istediğim, bunların hiçbiri benim ilgime layık değil. Endişelenmene gerek yok. Artık seninle ilgilenmiyorum."
